If you'd like to watch more
inspirational programming,

00:59:41.320 --> 00:59:43.300 align:middle line:10%
check out
"Inspirations" on Gaia.

00:59:43.300 --> 00:59:48.070 align:middle line:10%
I am Lisa Garr, and I
invite you to stay aware.

